data.description: ABSOLUTELY FABULOUS RUE MAISON HOME!!  So much space, and so many details in this 4 bedroom, 3 bath home in an exclusive gated community in south Abilene with classic details that you will fall in love with, wonderful front courtyard and grand entry leading into a gorgeous sitting area with tiled bar area and a grand indoor Juliet balcony, large living area open to dining, downstairs en suite, upstairs en suite, plus 2 other bedrooms, and an upstairs sitting area overlooking the downstairs sitting area, 2 car garage, and wonderful outdoor patios, plus a community clubhouse and pool!
